articles.author: Joey Klender
articles.title: Tesla launches GigaBier: Cybertruck-inspired pilsner - TESLARATI
articles.description: Tesla has launches its second venture into alcohol with GigaBier, now available in Europe (sorry U.S. fans).
articles.content:
Tesla has launched GigaBier, a Cybertruck-inspired Pilsner that is available in the European market.
